	1.	Permissions: list exact origins, never <all_urls>.
	2.	CSP: script-src 'self'; object-src 'none'.
	3.	Content scripts only relay sanitized messages.
	4.	Validate each message & sender.
	5.	No unsafe DOM APIs; use textContent.
	6.	HTTPS fetch only; tokens in storage.session.
	7.	Audit deps; block critical CVEs in CI.
	8.	Deterministic build; review manifest diff before publish.